			<h1><span style=3D"color: #000080;"><strong>2026 Slate of Officers And G=
eneral Members Meeting</strong></span></h1>
<p>The General Member=E2=80=99s meeting will take place on Tuesday November=
 18 beginning at 6PM. Members will receive an email with the agenda and Zoo=
m connection information. &nbsp;Pursuant to Article VIII of the PHRF SoCal =
Bylaws, below is the proposed 2026 Slate of Officers. Members in good stand=
ing who would like to run for any of these positions, please send an email =
to the Fleet Administrator identifying the position you=E2=80=99d like to r=
un for. Voting will take place during the meeting.</p>
<p>2026 Proposed Slat of Officers</p>
<p>=E2=80=93 PRESIDENT =E2=80=93 ROBERT (BOB) LANGAN (DWYC =E2=80=93 AREA E=
/F)<br>
=E2=80=93 VICE PRESIDENT =E2=80=93 DANIEL MURPHY (CYC =E2=80=93 AREA B)<br>
=E2=80=93 JUDGE ADVOCATE =E2=80=93 LISA GILINGER (SBYC =E2=80=93 AREA I)<br=
>
=E2=80=93 TREASURER =E2=80=93 ROBER (BOB) HUBBARD (SlBYC =E2=80=93 AREA C)<=
br>
=E2=80=93 CHIEF HANDICAPPER =E2=80=93 DAVID CATTLE (CRA =E2=80=93 AREA G)<b=
r>
=E2=80=93 VICE HANDICAPPER =E2=80=93 PAUL KATZ (DRYC =E2=80=93 AREA B)<br>
=E2=80=93 DATA SYSTEMS MANAGER =E2=80=93 SUE GRIESBACH (DWYC =E2=80=93 AREA=
 E/F)</p>
<hr>
<h1><span style=3D"color: #000080;"><strong>Latest Regional Meeting Minutes=
</strong></span></h1>
<p>The October regional meeting minutes were posted <a href=3D"https://phrf=
socal.org/wp-content/uploads/RegionalMeetingsArchive/lm.pdf">here</a> on No=
vember 14, starting the 7-day opposition period. A summary of the rating ch=
anges is posted to the right under =E2=80=9CRating Reviews.=E2=80=9D Any op=
position to these ratings should be addressed to the Fleet Secretary before=
 the opposition window closes.</p>
<p>The agenda for upcoming regional meetings goes out in an email to member=
s and subscribers about one week prior to the meeting date.&nbsp; It is usu=
ally posted to the website a few days before the meeting.&nbsp; You can fin=
d the latest agenda <a href=3D"https://www.phrfsocal.org/wp-content/uploads=
/RegionalMeetingsArchive/la.pdf">here</a>.</p>
<p>To see all the regional agendas and minutes go to the archive <a href=3D=
"https://phrfsocal.org/regional-meeting-archives/">here</a>.</p>
<hr>
<h1><span style=3D"color: #000080;"><strong>Latest Changes to Rules</strong=
></span></h1>
<p>The rules were last updated in November, 2023.&nbsp; You can find a summ=
ary of the changes and the latest rules document <a href=3D"https://phrfsoc=
al.org/index.php/rules-bylaws/">here</a>.</p>
<hr>
<h1><span style=3D"color: #000080;"><strong>Latest Area Meeting Minutes</st=
rong></span></h1>
